ucida grande&#39;, tahoma, sans-serif;line-height:24.049999237060547px;background:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\">质地清透，淡淡的香薰味让你爱上敷它过夜的感觉。</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:13px;text-indent:2em;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, &#39;lucida grande&#39;, tahoma, sans-serif;line-height:24.049999237060547px;background:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><strong>双重配方联合作用：</strong></p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:13px;text-indent:2em;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, &#39;lucida grande&#39;, tahoma, sans-serif;line-height:24.049999237060547px;background:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\">净化配方可深层保湿、淡化瑕疵，使肤色均匀亮丽；</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:13px;text-indent:2em;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, &#39;lucida grande&#39;, tahoma, sans-serif;line-height:24.049999237060547px;background:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\">活力配方在睡眠时补给氧气，一觉醒来，光感净透，还原亮白水嫩肤色。</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:13px;text-indent:2em;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, &#39;lucida grande&#39;, tahoma, sans-serif;line-height:24.049999237060547px;background:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\">主要成分：水、光果甘草提取物、甘油、角鲨烷、松露萃取液、丁二醇、天然石榴（PUNICA GRANATUM）籽提取物、海藻糖、细小裸藻多糖类、神经酰胺3、葡聚糖、木糖醇、聚丙烯酸酯交联聚合物-6、卡波姆、三乙醇胺、透明质酸钠、尿囊素</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:13px;text-indent:2em;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, &#39;lucida grande&#39;, tahoma, sans-serif;line-height:24.049999237060547px;background:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\">净化配方：水、甘油、葡聚糖、</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:13px;text-indent:2em;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 微软雅黑, arial, &#39;lucida grande&#39;, tahoma, sans-serif;line-height:24.049999237060547px;background:#ffffff;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\">活力配方：细小裸藻多糖类</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:13px;text-indent:2em;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#3