kground-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\" /><span style=\"line-height:25px;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">5、货源图片（准备至少三张货源图片）</span><br style=\"line-height:25px;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\" /><span style=\"line-height:25px;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">6、一张漂亮的封面图</span></p>','0',NULL,'141','0','1','1423028190','1435916510');");
