indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;【一膜两样——产品成分及分析】&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　【多肽净肌水光面膜】（30ml*4片）&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　&nbsp;主要成分：&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　奥氏海藻提取物、银耳提取物、芦荟提取物、棕榈酰三肽-1、棕榈酰四肽-7、棕榈酰五肽-4、北美金缕梅提取物、马齿苋提取物、透明质酸钠、卡波姆、尿囊素等。&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　功效：&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　及时改善肌肤缺水干燥，实现吸水、活水、储水、锁水、使肌肤如水般润泽。深度清洁，净化污垢，隐匿毛孔，舒缓清润，减少黑头和粉刺产生，重现健康光泽。通透毛孔，提亮肤色，令肌肤光洁细腻。淡化细纹干纹，改善肌肤松弛弹性，收紧脸部轮廓，塑造水光灵动之美。&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　【多肽驻颜复苏面膜】（30ml*2片）&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　主要成分：&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　金盏花提取物、北美金缕梅提取物、乳酸钠、三肽-1、六肽-9、棕榈酰三肽-1、棕榈酰四肽-7、棕榈酰五肽-4、乙酰基六肽-8、九泰-1，光果甘草提取物、雪莲花提取物、邹波角叉菜粉、尿囊素、黄原胶、透明质酸钠等。&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　功效：&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　深度滋养肌肤，改善干燥、暗沉、松弛、脆弱等肌肤衰退痕迹。平滑细纹，令肌肤饱满Q弹、轮廓坚实如塑、青春逆转。提亮肤色，减缓肌肤暗沉、令肌肤光泽亮丽、细腻柔滑。修复受损肌肤、淡化印痕，改善毛孔，复苏盎然生机机。&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　价格对比：零售价128元，同类产品中具备绝对价格优势！&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /><br style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#f2f3f5;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font:14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体;word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />　　成分对比：补水保湿为纯植物原料，抗衰修复采用高端顶级肽类，更加科学满足顾客护肤需求。&nbsp;<br style=\"text-transform:none;background-c